column5: Hi, new to Simcoe and looking for a decent launch on cooks or holland river near the lake.  I have a 14 ft tinny if that helps.  I also have small kids, so am looking to stay away from gong show ramps if possible...easy in and easy out.  I am ok to pay a launch fee for less traffic.  Thanks in advance.
Which town? Bradford gilford or keswick?
Thinking Gilford.  Coming from Brampton and want some ice out perch and crappie
Unfortunatly i cant help with gilford, if you decide to come to the keswick side i live by some launchs and could help you out. Good luck
Ok..thanks.   There must be some guys who know Gilford?
